HELLO, MY NAME IS ZAKIR.

36 years young, husband and father, coffee addict. Highly motivated creative developer with international client portfolio.

In the early days of my career I worked in several agencies in London, ranging from website development to online marketing agencies. This allowed me to work with several large brands around London.

I currently work as a freelancer and spend most of my time crafting and working on awesome projects.
